# PC Network Pharmacology & Transcriptomics Analysis

Comprehensive analysis tools for Polygonum cuspidatum (虎杖, 호장근) network pharmacology and transcriptomics studies.

## Repository Structure

### DEG_analysis/
Differential expression gene (DEG) analysis and visualization tools

- **Volcano Plot Analysis** - volcano plots
- **KEGG Pathway Dot Plot** - Cardiometabolic pathway enrichment visualization  
- **Venn Diagram** - PC target & DEG overlap analysis

## Quick Start
```bash
git clone https://github.com/JihongOh/PC-netpharm-transcriptomics.git
cd PC-netpharm-transcriptomics/DEG_analysis
```
